Description.SourceString: Serving as the front line to the Republic Coastal Legion, long have Conquerors lived up to the namesake. These beasts are fitted with armaments to tackle threats both above and below, including a specialized sonar station and depth charge launchers. A young upstart, Diana Geminus, was first to command a Conqueror after quickly rising through the ranks with fresh ideas for defence against the northerner’s disgraceful efforts.
